Dataset Folder

This folder is used to store student face images for the Smart Face Attendance System.

Folder Structure:
- Each student should have a separate folder.
- Folder name format: RollNumber_Name

Example:
dataset/
└── 21A91A0501_Rohini/
    ├── 1.jpg
    ├── 2.jpg
    ├── 3.jpg

Image Guidelines:
- Use clear face images (passport-size preferred).
- One face per image.
- JPG format only.
- Minimum 2 images per student recommended.

Note:
Real student images are not included in this repository for privacy reasons.
